data = value['data']
	udt = {"tagType": "UdtType"}
	udt['name'] = value['name']
	
	baseFolderPath = value['baseFolderPath']
	tagProvider = value['tagProvider']
	derivedFrom = value['derivedFrom']
	udt['typeId'] = derivedFrom
	
	folders = {}
	def getTag(line):
		name = line['Tagname']
		dataType = line['DataType']
		documentation = line['Description']
		defaultValue = None
		tagType = "AtomicTag"
		valueSource = "memory"
		engUnit=line['engUnit']
		tag = {
		          "valueSource": valueSource,
		          "dataType": dataType,
		          "documentation": documentation,
		          "name": name,
		          "value": defaultValue,
		          "tagType": tagType
		        }
		#Create Scaling
		scaleMode = line['scaleMode']
		if scaleMode != 'None':
			tag['scaleMode'] = scaleMode
			tag['rawLo'] = line['rawLo']
			tag['rawHigh'] = line['rawHigh']
			tag['scaledLo'] = line['scaledLo']
			tag['scaledHigh'] = line['scaledHigh']
		#Create History
		historyEnabled = True#line['HistoryEnabled']
		if historyEnabled:
			tag['historyEnabled'] =True
			tag['historicalDeadbandStyle'] ='Discrete'
			tag['historyProvider'] = {"bindType": "parameter","binding": "{HistoryStorageProvider}"}
			tag['History Path'] =historyPath = {"bindType": "parameter","binding": "{HistoryModelPathPrefix}/{PathToTag}"}
		return tag
	
	#Get Folders
	for line in data:
		tagFolderPath = line['TagFolderPath']
		if tagFolderPath in folders:
			#create Tag
			tag = getTag(line)
			folder['tags'].append(tag)
		else:
			tag = getTag(line)
			folder = {"name": tagFolderPath,"tagType": "Folder"}
			folder['tags'] = [tag]
			folders[tagFolderPath] = folder
			
	udt['tags']=folders.values()	
	return udt

config.script:
# Create Logger
	logger = system.util.getLogger('UDT Generator')
	collisionPolicy = self.view.custom.collisionPolicy
	udtBase = self.view.custom.udtBase
	udtBase = dict(udtBase)
	tagProvider = self.view.custom.tagProvider
	
	#Configure Base UDT 
	baseTagPath = self.view.custom.baseFolderPath
	baseTagPath = '['+tagProvider+']_types_/'+baseTagPath
	results = system.tag.configure(baseTagPath, udtBase, collisionPolicy)
	self.view.custom.results=results
	system.perspective.print(results[0])
	if str(results[0])=="Good":
		
		#Configure Application UDT
		applicationFolderPath = self.view.custom.applicationFolderPath
		system.perspective.print(applicationFolderPath)
		udtApplication = self.view.custom.udtApplication
		
		udtApplication = dict(udtApplication)
		applicationFolderPath = '['+tagProvider+']_types_/'+applicationFolderPath
		applicationResults = system.tag.configure(applicationFolderPath, udtApplication, collisionPolicy)
		results.append(applicationResults)
